  <p class="gd-lede">Beyond Alaska, heliskiing in the continental United States is a smaller, more regulated world — a handful of permitted operations in Utah, Colorado and Nevada delivering dry Rocky Mountain powder. This guide covers where you can fly, how the land-use rules shape it, the season, cost and who it suits, and offers an honest look at our <a href="/iceland">Iceland</a> <a href="/packages">packages</a> as an alternative.</p>
